# Menstruation Tracker

A simple health-focused menstruation tracking web application built with React.  
Users can sign up, log in, track their cycles, view history, and get predictions for their next period and estimated fertile window.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- Email + password authentication (localStorage-based)
- Protected tracker area (only visible when logged in)
- Add, edit, and delete cycle entries
- Cycle predictions:
  - Last period start
  - Average cycle length
  - Next expected period
  - Estimated fertile window
- Persistent data using `localStorage`
- Simple, clean, and responsive user interface

---

